INSERT INTO txn_program_faqs (program_faq_id, program_id, question, answer, active, created_by, modified_by, created_at,
                              updated_at, created_ip, modified_ip)
VALUES (5, 2, 'I have high cholesterol. Will your weight loss program lower it?',
        'Absolutely! Our cholesterol weight loss program is designed to focus on lowering your bad cholesterol by including foods, spice mixes and infused waters. We ensure that you have a \''heart-healthy\'' diet to bring your blood cholesterol within a normal range.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (6, 2, 'Will you give me any supplements for my cholesterol?',
        'No, we only recommend a healthy, balanced diet. We will not give you any other supplements than what your doctor has prescribed. Once your cholesterol level comes down with our diet, you may visit your doctor to alter your medications.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (7, 2, 'Will my cholesterol level stay low even after I complete your program?',
        'As long as you continue eating healthy diet recommended in our program and do mild recommended exercises every day, you will be able to maintain your cholesterol levels within the normal range.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (8, 2, 'Do I have to give up some of my favourite foods?',
        'No, you don\''t have to give up on your favourite foods but you will be strictly monitored by us. You will have to lower the quantity of your favourite foods. You will also have to bring down the quantity of fatty foods from your diet.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (9, 17, 'Are there any side effects I should be aware of?',
        'No, there are no side effects whatsoever. Our programs, our food plans and our spice mixes and infused water are totally natural. They have been created in a simple but effective manner.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (10, 17, 'Can I stop taking the medicines my doctor prescribed me?',
        'You will lose weight with our program and it will lower your blood pressure but you will still have to take medication prescribed by your doctor to be on the safer side. But we can say that your medicine and your dosage will be reduced after you achieve a normal weight through our program.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (11, 17, 'Will your program cause any damage to my body?',
        'No, our programs are completely safe and nature based. And it is with guarantee we say that it will not harm your body. But you need to follow our program religiously or you will not see any improvement.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (12, 17, 'How does your program work?',
        'We start with changing your lifestyle and your food habits, we help you eat a balanced diet, to get your body working we recommend enough but light exercises, and we help you reduce your stress through our expert guidance.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (13, 4, 'Are there any side effects from your program?',
        ' No, there are no side effects from our programs. There are only good results from our program. We only adopt natural methods and recommend only natural foods for your health goal.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (14, 4, 'Do I have to eat less?',
        'No, you don\''t need to eat less and or starve or fast. Our natural, healthy foods and diet plans make sure that you are satiated and refreshed all day long.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (15, 4, 'My weight fluctuates. Do I need to do heavy exercises?',
        'Aah the challenges that Thyroid poses! But the good news is that you don\''t need to do heavy exercises. We recommend exercises that are neither heavy nor tiresome but rather just the right ones.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (16, 4, 'I am always travelling. Can I still reduce my weight?',
        'Of course, you can reduce weight. We have this amazing \''Traveller Menu\'' that is created for this very purpose. We made sure that this menu is suited for people who always love to travel or have to travel.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (17, 6, 'How will it help me?',
        'We use natural methods and personalised diet plans which will help you control high blood pressure, cholesterol and insulin levels. Rather than treating symptoms individually, our natural solutions get to the root of the problem. Our effective herbs help to detoxify your system, reduce bad cholesterol and counteract insulin resistance.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (18, 6, 'Will it improve my other problems like fatigues, hair fall, constipation, irritation etc.?',
        'As you begin your program and follow our detoxification and cleansing step, most of the symptoms subside and disappear from your body. You get to have a lifetime benefit of good health. Our recommended foods and herbs will cleanse your system and keep you refreshed.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (19, 6, 'How soon will I lose weight through your program?',
        'First of all, your body chemistry needs to be transformed in a manner that will lead to a permanent change. To heal the ravages of Syndrome X you must be dedicated in changing your lifestyle. But it takes time, commitment, persistence and patience on your part. Once you make this commitment, you are on your way to free Syndrome X.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-13 00:00:00', '2017-04-13 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (20, 3, 'How long will it be till I see some results?',
        'First of all, your hormonal imbalance needs to be corrected. You must be firm in changing your lifestyle to heal the damage of PCOS. All it takes is time, commitment, persistence and patience on your part. And slowly, you will see the results. You will be free from acne, you will have regular menstrual cycles, your weight will stabilise.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (21, 3, 'Is PCOS hereditary?',
        'Yes, to some extent PCOS is hereditary. But you need not lose hope and faith. Our weight loss program will try to eliminate your health condition from the core.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (22, 3, 'My weight keeps changing. Is doing heavy exercises necessary?',
        'There is nothing as challenging as PCOS! But, you do not need to do heavy exercises. We recommend light but effective exercises that eliminate the symptoms and heal your body from PCOS.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (23, 3, 'Do I have to stop my medications that my gynaecologist gave me?',
        'No, not at first, however once your hormonal imbalance is corrected and stabilised, you can consult your physician who can alter your medications.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (24, 7, 'I have diabetes. Can you help me?',
        'Yes, we can and we will. If you have diabetes type 2, we advise you right, proper and suitable diet and certain spice mixes and infused waters that balances your sugar levels. But if you have diabetes type 1, as of now, we are not taking it in our program.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (25, 7, 'Do I have to stop my medications during the program?',
        'No, not in the beginning, however once your levels are stable and within the range for a long period of time, your physician can alter your medications.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (26, 7, 'My doctor has already given me a diet. How different is your diet?',
        'Most diets described by doctors are pretty standard. They usually are a list of DOs and DONTs. But at NewMe, your plan will be more nutrient dense and individualized. This approach helps in maintaining your sugar levels faster and better.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (27, 7, 'Will my sugar levels stay normal even after completing your plan?',
        'Yes, your sugar level will stay normal as long as you continue to follow the advice provided by us.', TRUE, 1,
        1, '2017-04-14 00:00:00', '2017-04-14 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (28, 8, 'Can I get my cholesterol level any lower by changing my diet?',
        'A good start would be to compile a food diary. Be honest and write down everything you eat over a couple of weeks. Getting a good picture of your normal intake should help you to identify some positive changes you could make.<br/> Cut down on saturated fat wherever possible. Ideally an average woman should not exceed 20g per day (4 teaspoons of butter is around 10g of saturated fat). There are some key cholesterol busting foods that you could try with NewMe. We recommend a cholesterol free diet plan keeping your taste-buds in mind.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-16 00:00:00', '2017-04-16 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (29, 8, 'How do cholesterol levels change over a lifetime?',
        'It is true that cholesterol levels increase with age, and doctors know it is important to lower our lifetime exposure to cholesterol. So keeping your cholesterol low is important at all ages. As you get older your overall risk of circulatory disease increases. This is partly because of age and also due to other risk factors (high blood pressure, diabetes, weight gain) which may develop over time. Your doctor can explain your risk of having a heart attack and what you might do to reduce the risk. We at NewMe make sure that you maintain your cholesterol levels even after the program is over. We give you Maintenance Guides at the end of the program which can be used for lifetime.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-16 00:00:00', '2017-04-16 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (30, 8, 'I\''ve had a few tests and my HDL (good cholesterol) is relatively low. How can I increase it?',
        'Having a low HDL-cholesterol and a high triglyceride level is quite common and often happens when the body has difficulty in dealing with dietary fats after a meal. Smoking also depresses HDL-cholesterol. We recommend the following lifestyle approach to raise HDL levels. If you are a smoker it is best to stop. If you carry a lot of excess weight around your waist then losing some of this could help increase your HDL and reduce your triglyceride levels. We will help you in doing this. <br/>\r\nEat a balanced diet based on starchy wholegrain foods with plenty of fruit and vegetables, and low in saturated fat. Opt for cooking oils higher in the monounsaturated fats such as rapeseed oil and olive oil (but use sparingly if overweight) and include nuts and soya regularly.\r\n',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-16 00:00:00', '2017-04-16 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (31, 18, 'I have diabetes. Can you help me?',
        'Yes, we can and we will. If you have diabetes type 2, we advise you right, proper and suitable diet and certain spice mixes and infused waters that balances your sugar levels. But if you have diabetes type 1, as of now, we are not taking it in our program.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (32, 18, 'Do I have to stop my medications during the program?',
        'No, not in the beginning, however once your levels are stable and within the range for a long period of time, your physician can alter your medications.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (33, 18, 'My doctor has already given me a diet. How different is your diet?',
        'Most diets described by doctors are pretty standard. They usually are a list of DOs and DONTs. But at NewMe, your plan will be more nutrient dense and individualized. This approach helps in maintaining your sugar levels faster and better.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (34, 18, 'Will my sugar levels stay normal even after completing your plan?',
        'Yes, your sugar level will stay normal as long as you continue to follow the advice provided by us.', TRUE, 1,
        1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (35, 10, 'Are there any side effects from your program?',
        'No, there are no side effects from our programs. There are only good results from our program. We only adopt natural methods and recommend only natural foods for your health goal.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (36, 10, 'Do I have to eat less?',
        'No, you don\''t need to eat less and or starve or fast. Our natural and health foods and diet plans make sure that you are satiated and refreshed all day long.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (37, 10, 'My weight fluctuates. Do I need to do heavy exercises?',
        'Aah the challenges that Thyroid poses! But the good news is that you don\''t need to do heavy exercises. We recommend exercises that are neither heavy nor tiresome but rather just the right ones.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (38, 10, 'I am always travelling. Can I still reduce my weight?',
        'Of course, you can reduce weight. We have this amazing <strong>Traveller Menu </strong> that is created for this very purpose. We made sure that this menu is suited for people who always love to travel or have to travel.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (39, 12, 'Who would gain from this program',
        'Anyone suffering from recurrent cough & cold allergies, bronchi fever or sinusitis will gain from this program.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (40, 12, 'How can you help?',
        'We give you personalised plans depending on your lifestyle, body type and age. Your everyday diet consists of rich vitamin and mineral antioxidants that will combat the effect of radicals. Also, therapeutic waters and herbs help cleanse your body and improve resistance to diseases.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (41, 12, 'I feel tired all the time. How can you help?',
        'We correct your good pattern to one that is rich in antioxidants. It takes care of the deficiency caused by store, thereby preventing tiredness and irritation. We suggest right quantity of food and herbs that will cleanse your system and help you feel fresh.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (42, 12, 'I am already taking many vitamin A without any success. How would your program help?',
        'If your body is loaded with toxins then no amount of vitamin A can help you. Your body will regain its absorptive power only with detoxification. Detoxification is the first step to all plans. Please check our \"How it works\" page for more information on how we recommend our plans.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (43, 12, 'How different will I feel after the program?',
        'We would love to give you energy of a kid but of course age plays its own role. Once you finish our program, your body will feel lighter and you will be able to perform your daily tasks without feeling tired and fatigued. Your energy level will rise and give you power to work better and faster than before.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (44, 15, 'I have been suffering from gas and acidity for a long time?',
        'It may be because of the food and your lifestyle that interferes with digestion. We at NewMe, identify the root cause and treat it through herbs, therapeutic waters and customised food plan.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (45, 15, 'I take antacids every day ,still my stomach burns everyday. How can you help me?',
        'Antacid gives temporary relief but root cause remains untreated. We use our recommended food as medicine to remove toxins, cleanse and nourish your body.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (46, 15,
        'All my life I had a balanced diet but since two years I have gas and bloating even with the same diet. What is the remedy?',
        'As you age, your nutrients need change and so does your digestion. We therefore suggest a customised plan with natural herbs which will re-energise your whole body.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2017-04-17 00:00:00', '2017-04-17 00:00:00', ':0', ':0'),
       (55, 1,
        'I am overweight. Will your program work for me? What if I don\''t lose weight even after following the program?',
        'Our weight loss program will definitely work for you. We have a success rate of 98%. Our approach to weight loss is different from others. It is completely focused and individualised. We start by correcting your eating habits and helping you to eat the right foods. That is why diets recommended by us are 10/10.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2018-11-19 13:33:24', '2018-11-19 13:33:24', ':0', ':0'),
       (56, 1, 'Once I start losing weight will my skin sag and become dull, will I have wrinkles?',
        'No, neither will your skin become dull or sag nor will you have any wrinkles. In fact, your skin complexion will improve and will have a angelic glow on it. Our food plan customised for you will be fibre rich, less fatty and nutrient dense.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2018-11-19 13:33:24', '2018-11-19 13:33:24', ':0', ':0'),
       (57, 1,
        'I previously enrolled with a dietitian for a weight loss program, lost weight but put it back again. Can you guarantee me positive results?',
        'Our program is not a diet but a complete lifestyle change. When you leave a diet program, you will put on weight. But our weight loss program makes you knowledgeable of your individual body type and the type of food you should eat. Once the knowledge is shared with you, you will never lose your way again and never put on weight. We will be giving free maintenance kits to you for your lifetime so that you remain motivated and never look back to your old life.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2018-11-19 13:33:24', '2018-11-19 13:33:24', ':0', ':0'),
       (58, 1, 'Will I lose fat from specific areas?',
        'No, we are truly sad to say this. You cannot lose fat only in your problematic areas. There isn\''t any program of any kind that guarantees spot reduction. It is a gradual process. We help you by recommending the right food and right exercises that reduces the excess fat slowly and in an overall manner. Slowly these problematic areas will start showing effect and you will start to lose weight.',
        TRUE, 1, 1, '2018-11-19 13:33:24', '2018-11-19 13:33:24', ':0', ':0');

